data.name: 0001 (388.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)

data.name: 0003 (388.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)

data.name: 0006 (388.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: $10Considering this is Miss Suzumiya, #W50…#W10…#W10$8I somehow doubt it'll be so easy.

data.name: 0008 (388.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: $10Instead, #W10my seasoned intuition is giving me a stern warning—

data.value: $10What?

data.name: 0013 (388.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: $10That so-called data lifeform—#W30are there any others?

data.name: 0014 (388.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: $10They exist.

data.name: 0015 (388.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: $10Currently, the confirmable population is—

data.name: 0016 (388.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: $10H-hold on! #W20$7You don't have to say it!

data.name: 0017 (388.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: $10I was dangerously close to hearing something I don't want to know.

data.name: 0018 (388.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: $8This is my personal opinion but, #W20If we're done after only three, #W70I'd rather do more.

data.name: 0022 (388.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: $6How long are you gonna make me wait! #W10Kyon!

data.name: 0023 (388.ja) KYON (キョン)

data.name: 0024 (388.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: $8And I'll tell you what, #W20$7I'm not happy with this at all!

data.name: 0025 (388.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: $8To begin with, #W10what I want is #W10a mystery worthy of the new seven wonders.

data.name: 0026 (388.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)

data.name: 0027 (388.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)

data.name: 0030 (388.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: $9Koizumi—what's next?

data.name: 0031 (388.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)

data.name: 0033 (388.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
